::Firaxis::
       "All right they're not coming."  He shakes his head as he looks at the 
empty bridge.  He slaps a comlink down on a table in front of SFC.  "Use this 
to contact me if you need anything.  I'll be out seeing a friend of mine."  
He leaves the Autobot base and sends a message to Meteara.  "I've been 
wondering if you've thought anymore about what I said?  I'm on my way to see 
you as soon as I can figure out where you are.  Oh, and I'm bringing my new 
dog along too."

--part1_16f.e4075da.2a257d01_boundary
